Description: Comprehensive toolkit for Synthetic Control Methods (SCM) with advanced 
    features including specification curve analysis, CatBoost+SHAP machine learning 
    analysis, and multiple inference procedures. The package highlight is specification 
    curves colored by SHAP values showing feature relevance to predicted treatment effects. 
    Provides functions for data preparation, model estimation, statistical inference 
    (including SCPI and placebo-based methods), and publication-ready visualizations. 
    Supports multiple outcome models (OLS, Ridge, Lasso, Augmented Synthetic Control) 
    and includes parallel processing capabilities for large-scale specification curve analysis.
